OL,5, Staff at Tesco stores are to be offered
OL,6, body cameras amid a rise in violent    
OL,7, attacks, the supermarket's chief       
OL,8, executive has said.                    
OL,10,FThe company has seen physical assaults 
OL,11,Fincrease by a third since last year.   
OL,13,FIt mirrors findings by the British     
OL,14,FRetail Consortium (BRC) published      
OL,15,Fearlier this year, which found abuse   
OL,16,Fagainst retail staff had almost doubled
OL,17,Fcompared to pre-Covid levels.          
OL,19,FSimilar action has already been taken  
OL,20,Fby Sainsbury's, Waitrose and Co-op.    
